reviewText: Didn't know what to expect from this move. It was still very hokey, but a goof watch none the les. The ending battle was fantastic.

It's on you tube.
Watch the whole movie with subtitles then decide if you want to buy it. I did.
It's definitely more of a FOX kids Utraman Tiga type feel to it but enjoyable none the less.
i like the ultraman series and would continue to get the new movies when they come out i would recomend it to any ultraman fans

This is one of the best movies I have ever seen!  Being a tokusatsu fan, I had to see this movie & especially have it to "rightfully label myself" an Ultraman fan.  The only problem I have are the subs do not quite sound the best, thus I knocked off a point from my rating just for that minor inconvenience (I could understand the subtitles with those minor flaws, anyways)
